# Workspace map

## Read order (new task)
1. ADR: `documentation/ADR/index.md` — relevant only, not full catalog
2. Service spec: `documentation/specifications/microservices/<group>/<service>/`
3. Code: `application/<group>/<service>/`
4. Do not scan whole workspace — follow this map
5. **`application/` tasks:** skill `microservice-defaults` + rule `microservice-implementation.mdc` + `reference.md`. No repo exploration; do not open `currencies-crud` unless asked

